Tool Used

Apache JMeter

Objective

To evaluate application performance under load conditions.

Test Scenario

Virtual Users: 50

Ramp-Up Time: 10 seconds

Test Duration: 5 minutes

Metrics Observed
Metric	Result
Average Response Time	1.8 seconds
Error Rate	2%
Throughput	Stable
Observations

Application handled normal load efficiently

Slight delay observed during peak requests

Conclusion & Recommendation

The system performs well under moderate load. Performance can be improved by optimizing server response handling.
